title: Rob Portman Family Dinner
description:
Written by Zack Phillips
Starring: Dan Hodapp, Avery Monsen, Kelly Hudson, Jonathan Marballi, Lisa Kleinman

Directed by Jim Santangeli

From Maude Night at the Upright Citizens Brigade Theatre, May 8, 2013.

Filmed by Tom Levin, Curtis Raye.
Edited by Curtis Raye.
